data.description: Country livin’ at this beautiful 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath house! Situated on over two acres with a huge, flat back yard. Two huge master suites, one on the main floor, one on the second level. Granite countertops and hardwood floors! Partially finished basement, with ample amounts of storage. New HVAC system. Home also has a brand new, open floor plan, attached in-law suite. Suite has one huge bedroom and 1.5 bath. With a separate side entrance, the in-law suite has great AIRBNB potential, or rental opportunities.
